aboutMsg: I am a motivated programmer whose passion lies in coding and the world of technology. Over the past years, I have gained significant experience and knowledge in C#, PHP, and TypeScript. I continuously strive to enhance my skills in programming languages and stay up-to-date with the current trends in the industry. One of my greatest strengths is excelling in teamwork. I always enjoy being part of a team where we can share ideas and support each other's growth. I value collaboration, effective communication, and the efficient execution of projects. I possess excellent problem-solving skills and adaptability to new situations.
name: Tibor Blascsok
